 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-picture field-type-imagefield-crop field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Picture:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://nashvillemusicians.org/sites/default/files/18033851_632193963641553_1981783234055860594_n.jpg&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;150&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-contact-information field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Contact Information:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;For booking contact 615 403 4419 or email at tim@timmcdonaldband.com&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-personnel-instrumentation field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Personnel/Instrumentation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The Tim McDonald is comprised of piano, guitar, bass, drums, vocals and harmony vocals.  The Tim McDonald Band is ever evolving with the Who&amp;#039;s Who 1st call musicians.  Tim performs all genres and focus&amp;#039;s on Country, Red Dirt and Southern Rock.  Tim also performs solo on his piano, duo with guitar and trio with piano bass and drums.  The Tim McDonald Band is a perfect fit for any situation and musical needs from private parties to small rooms and main stages.  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-describe-what-you-do-in-10 field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Describe &amp;quot;What You Do&amp;quot; in 100 Words or Less:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Tim McDonald has toured with the legends of Country, Pop and Jazz artist including Olivia Newton John, Blake Shelton, Pam Tillis, Hank Williams Jr., Mark Chesnutt and many more.  Tim is currently focusing on his solo career and enjoys performing his original and cover music for audiences of all types.  Book Tim today for your musical needs or come see a show when you&amp;#039;re in the Nashville area.  Shows, soundclips etc. available at www.timmcdonaldband.com&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-musical-style-s- field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Musical Style(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/cover-tunes&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Cover Tunes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/original-music&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Original Music&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/music-dancing&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Music for Dancing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/music-listening&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Music for Listening&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/requests&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Requests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&